Nova Skin v2 License Notice

Version: v2

Nova Skin is a the tree skin based on the Liberty skin structure and implementation.

This skin was made from the Liberty skin lineage, including thetree-skin-liberty, and keeps compatibility-oriented concepts such as the document tools, search form, recent activity sidebar, configurable logo, and wiki settings workflow.

Original projects:
- Liberty Skin: https://github.com/librewiki/liberty-skin
- thetree-skin-liberty: https://github.com/wjdgustn/thetree-skin-liberty

Liberty Skin is distributed under the GPL 3.0 license. Portions derived from Liberty Skin and related projects remain subject to their original licenses and notices. If modified Liberty-derived portions are distributed, the corresponding modified source code must be made available under the same GPL 3.0 terms. Anyone distributing a modified Nova Skin v2 should comply with the GPL 3.0 obligations for the Liberty-derived portions and related changes.

Nova-specific changes are provided as part of this skin package.
